These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, soy-milk
Sport: skiing, sailing, basketball, cricket
1. Beverage:sprite is on the right of Sport:basketball##1
2. Sport:cricket is on the far left##1
3. Sport:basketball is between Sport:sailing and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
4. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk is between Beverage:hot-chocolate and Beverage:sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk | sprite       |
| Sport      | cricket | skiing | basketball   | sailing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: filmmaking, hiking, fishing, baking
Nationality: indonesian, egyptian, german, japanese
1. Nationality:japanese is between Hobby:fishing and Nationality:egyptian##2
2. Hobby:baking is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:indonesian##1
4. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Nationality:indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | filmmaking | fishing | baking |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | japanese   | indonesian | german       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
