2. Nationality:argentine is between Nationality:indonesian and Food:peach##2
3. Nationality:indonesian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:american is on the left of Food:radish##1
5. Food:peach == Nationality:american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | strawberry    | asparagus | peach   | radish  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine   | american | thai |

