2. Pet:snake is between Sport:sailing and Pet:rabbit##2
3. Sport:swimming is on the far right##1
4. Pet:snake is on the right of Sport:snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rabbit   | snake    | hedgehog       | hamster   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | parkour | sailing | swimming |

